  file             = {Bennie et al. - 2008 - Slope, aspect and climate Spatially explicit and .pdf:EcoTime Machine/Slope, Aspect and Climate_ Spatially Explicit and Implicit Models of Topographic Microclimate in Chalk Grassland_Bennie2008.pdf:PDF},
